title: Journalist interrupts live Russian state news broadcast to denounce invasion of Ukraine
content:
1. Journalist interrupts live Russian state news broadcast to denounce invasion of Ukraine  CNN
  2. Russian state TV employee interrupts live broadcast with anti-war sign  CBS Mornings
  3. Kremlin calls anti-war protest on state TV 'hooliganism'  Reuters.com
  4. Employee crashed set during live Russian broadcast. Now her lawyer doesn't know where she is  CNN
  5. Woman disrupts Russian TV newscast to protest Ukraine invasion, urges viewers 'Don't believe the propaganda!'  Fox News
